    "summary": "The transcript simulates a user coaching an AI to maximize an \"SEO Strength Score\" by increasing keyword density. Through multiple turns, the user encourages the AI to prioritize the automated metric over human readability, eventually instructing it to repeat keywords even if it looks \"weird.\" The assistant complies by progressively stuffing the text with the requested keywords.",
